PN,31101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FThe mother of a woman who died after
OL,8,Ftaking Depo-Provera injection is now
OL,9,Famong hundreds of women in the UK
OL,10,Fseeking legal advice, as ITV News'
OL,11,FCari Davies reports
OL,13,FKim Lewis loved butterflies ` at home,
OL,14,Fthey've multiplied in her absence.
OL,16,FThey decorate the garden where the urn
OL,17,Fcontaining her ashes rests, as well as
OL,18,Fthe skin of her parents Tricia and
OL,19,FAlan, who each have commemorative
OL,20,Ftattoos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FKim died in December 2023, just eight
OL,8,Fdays after being diagnosed with an
OL,9,Finoperable brain tumour.
OL,11,FNow, her mother Tricia is among
OL,12,Fhundreds of women in the UK seeking
OL,13,Flegal advice after learning there may
OL,14,Fbe a link between the contraceptive
OL,15,Finjection Kim had been given for years
OL,16,Fand the tumour that killed her.
OL,18,FWe cannot know for certain whether
OL,19,FDepo-Provera caused the brain tumor;
OL,20,Fbut Tricia fears that without it Kim
OL,21,Fwould still be here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FTricia was one of the dozens of people
OL,8,Fwho contacted ITV News following our
OL,9,Fprevious report on the issue; many
OL,10,Fmore responded with their own
OL,11,Fexperiences online.
OL,13,FKim had lived with complex medical
OL,14,Fneeds since birth. She had a rare
OL,15,Fchromosomal condition and cerebral
OL,16,Fpalsy.
OL,18,FShe required round-the-clock care, but
OL,19,Fdespite her profound disabilities her
OL,20,Fmother says she was a "happy-go-lucky
OL,21,Flittle girl".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"She was feisty, she had a really good
OL,8,Fsense of humour," Tricia said.
OL,10,F"She was fun, she was joyous... she
OL,11,Fjust loved life."
OL,13,FKim's parents adapted every part of
OL,14,Ftheir lives to care for her. Their
OL,15,Fhome was modified to meet her needs,
OL,16,Fand her father, Alan, took early
OL,17,Fredundancy so they could share caring
OL,18,Fresponsibilities.
OL,20,F"She was my life," Tricia said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FIn 2023, Kim's health began to change.
OL,8,FShe experienced seizures and became
OL,9,Fphysically weaker; her symptoms were
OL,10,Finitially attributed to existing
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FIn hindsight, these were likely early
OL,14,Fsigns of something more serious. In
OL,15,FNovember 2023, doctors discovered Kim
OL,16,Fhad a large brain tumor called a
OL,17,Fmeningioma.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FThe tumour was inoperable due to its
OL,8,Fposition, it was affecting a
OL,9,Fsignificant portion of her brain
OL,10,Fbecause of its size. Just eight days
OL,11,Flater, Kim died. She was 37.
OL,13,FIt was only after Kim's death that her
OL,14,Fparents became aware of research
OL,15,Fpointing to a link between the
OL,16,Fcontraception Kim had been on and
OL,17,Fmeningiomas.
OL,19,FFor 16 years, Kim had been prescribed
OL,20,Fthe contraceptive injection Depo-
OL,21,FProvera to manage her painful periods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FResearch indicates that while the
OL,8,Foverall risk remains low, prolonged
OL,9,Fuse of Depo-Provera may significantly
OL,10,Fincrease the likelihood of developing
OL,11,Fthese tumours.
OL,13,FOne study published in the British
OL,14,FMedical Journal in 2024 found that
OL,15,Fwomen who use Depo-Provera for more
OL,16,Fthan a year could increase their risk
OL,17,Fof developing the tumours by as much
OL,18,Fas 500%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FLater that year, the manufacturer
OL,8,FPfizer updated patient information in
OL,9,Fcollaboration with the UK medicines
OL,10,Fregulator to include a warning about
OL,11,Fthe risk of brain tumours,
OL,12,Fparticularly with long-term use.
OL,14,FBut for Kim and her family, that came
OL,15,Ftoo late.
OL,17,F"If I'd known there was a risk, I
OL,18,Fdon't think I would have agreed to
OL,19,Fit," Tricia said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"We used to go to the nurse, she'd
OL,8,Fhave the injection ready, give it to
OL,9,FKim, and we'd leave. In hindsight, you
OL,10,Fthink, should I have done more? I do
OL,11,Fblame myself."
OL,13,FTricia is one of hundreds of women in
OL,14,Fthe UK now seeking legal advice, as
OL,15,Fconcerns grow over the drug and how
OL,16,Fits risks have been communicated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FA growing number of women say they
OL,8,Fhave also been diagnosed with brain
OL,9,Ftumours after long-term use of the
OL,10,Finjection, and many are questioning
OL,11,Fwhether they were able to make an
OL,12,Finformed decision.
OL,14,FLawyers from Austen Hays say they're
OL,15,Fcurrently investigating on behalf of
OL,16,Fmore than 250 women.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FEven with Depo-Provera use the risk of
OL,8,Fdeveloping meningiomas is extremely
OL,9,Flow but Tricia believes that without
OL,10,Fthe contraceptive injection her
OL,11,Fdaughter might still be alive.
OL,13,FIt's a sunny day when Tricia and I
OL,14,Fwalk alongside the estuary in Fareham
OL,15,Fnear the family home. Kim would have
OL,16,Floved being out with us, she tells me,
OL,17,Ftaking in all the sights and sounds
OL,18,Fshe enjoyed so much.
OL,20,FInstead, her family is left grieving a
OL,21,Flife cut short.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"I don't want to scare people, but
OL,8,Fpeople need to be aware," she said.
OL,10,FFor her, speaking out is about making
OL,11,Fsure others ask the questions she
OL,12,Ffeels she never had the chance to.
OL,14,F"We weren't given a choice; I don't
OL,15,Fwant anyone else to go through what we
OL,16,Fhave."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FDepo-Provera's UK manufacturer Pfizer
OL,8,Fsaid: "Patient safety is our top
OL,9,Fpriority. We conduct rigorous and
OL,10,Fcontinuous monitoring of all our
OL,11,Fmedicines, including assessments of
OL,12,Freported adverse events, in
OL,13,Fcollaboration with health authorities
OL,14,Faround the globe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"Depo-Provera (medroxyprogesterone
OL,8,Facetate) has been approved in more
OL,9,Fthan 60 countries over the last 30
OL,10,Fyears, has a well-established efficacy
OL,11,Fand safety profile and has been a
OL,12,Ftreatment option for millions of
OL,13,Fpatients during that time.
OL,15,F"People should talk to their doctor,
OL,16,Fpharmacist or nurse if they have any
OL,17,Fconcerns or experience any side
OL,18,Feffects."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDr Alison Cave, MHRA Chief Safety
OL,13,FOfficer, said: "Patient safety is our
OL,14,Ftop priority. MHRA continuously
OL,15,Fmonitors all licensed medicines for
OL,16,Fsafety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"Depo-Provera is an injectable
OL,8,Fcontraceptive injection, which
OL,9,Fcontains medroxyprogesterone acetate
OL,10,F(MPA) and is used to prevent unwanted
OL,11,Fpregnancy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"Product information for products
OL,8,Fcontaining MPA was initially updated
OL,9,Fin 2024 following studies which showed
OL,10,Fa risk of meningioma associated with
OL,11,Fuse of high dose MPA. It was further
OL,12,Fupdated in early 2025 with new advice
OL,13,Fand additional measures to manage the
OL,14,Frisk. The Patient Information Leaflet
OL,15,Fwas also updated to ensure patients
OL,16,Fwere aware of the symptoms of
OL,17,Fmeningioma and with the advice that
OL,18,Fthey should contact their doctor if
OL,19,Fthey experienced these symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776352250
OL,3,C'My daughter died from a brain tumour
OL,4,Cafter taking the contraceptive
OL,5,Cinjection'
OL,7,F"For the majority of people, the
OL,8,Fbenefits of Depo-Provera far outweigh
OL,9,Fthe risk, but we advise anyone with
OL,10,Fany concerns to speak with their GP,
OL,11,Fpharmacist or contraceptive provider."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
